                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-42-18521122 t18521122-42-punishment-33"></join>Transported for Ten Years</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">There were two other indictments against the prisoner.</hi>)</p>
